01:29:36.880 --> 01:29:41.715
I bathe him.
I know every inch of his body.

01:29:41.800 --> 01:29:43.756
He doesn't have it.

01:29:43.840 --> 01:29:48.356
If the sign isn't visible,
then it must be hidden beneath the hair.

01:29:48.440 --> 01:29:51.796
Remove that, you'll find the number.

01:29:51.880 --> 01:29:54.519
What about the woman, the nanny?

01:29:54.600 --> 01:29:58.513
